  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "HR Executive",
  "description": "<p><u>Payroll Processing</u>:</p><ul><li>Assist in the preparation and processing of monthly payroll.</li><li>Ensure accurate entry of employee data, including new hires, terminations, and changes in employment status.</li><li>Verify and reconcile payroll discrepancies and resolve any issues promptly.</li></ul><p><u>Record Keeping:</u></p><ul><li>Maintain accurate payroll records and ensure data integrity in HRIS systems.</li><li>Prepare and distribute payroll reports as needed.</li></ul><p><u>Compliance:</u></p><ul><li>Assist in ensuring compliance with labor laws and regulations related to payroll and employment.</li><li>Support annual audits and provide necessary documentation.</li></ul><p><u>Employee Support</u>:</p><ul><li>Address employee inquiries related to payroll, benefits, and HR policies.</li><li>Provide assistance in onboarding new employees and managing benefits enrollment.</li><li>Administrative Tasks:</li><li>Support HR initiatives and projects as needed.</li><li>Assist in maintaining employee files and other HR documentation.</li><li>Perform any other related tasks or projects as assigned by the HR Manager.</li></ul>",
